{"tid":176112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友令我好煩惱","createTime":"2017-03-28T03:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T04:24:09.000Z","uid":80042,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfbd18f66822b03cb5a707cb287f65c9661e4fd1","tid":176112,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"女友月入萬中，我萬中，旅行AA <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說每次同女友旅行，我地都幾乎AA.<br />\n我會預先俾晒錢，之後再收返佢尾數，假設每個人7000左右。我都會考慮佢太大吃，叫佢可以食少D。但佢食量比我更高，食少D都得掛。每次去完旅行就同我呻食左好多野，意思即係叫我話比佢聽佢唔肥，唉！我從來都無要求佢食d咩唔得，不過有時最多一包糖一個雪糕。每次我叫佢食少D我都好唔開心，好似只係食先係佢既人生。而我地平時食飯係呃鬼我俾，雖然都只係譚仔。<br />\n大家覺得係我問題定佢問題，定無問題<br />\n我同佢拍左三年拖啦，我見其他朋友的女朋友食咩食咩，唔食既都有，我係羨慕，但我從不要求，我會覺得只要我錫佢就得,但有時現實下來，佢好似愛佢既野食多過我！"},{"pid":"4309e23201d8a1d4c8659dea5d41098b8be38b29","tid":176112,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:47:03.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c558f3806ef0b7fa7e42b5af0ca0aab5f62fa823","tid":176112,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好慘<br />\n佢成日淨係掛住食"},{"pid":"a86f2f4fb41ce964da3e56525286848a2ee4c2b6","tid":176112,"uid":43306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437a60c67d72c7f46917be640c98007fdba38a14","tid":176112,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"佢唔肥就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb79364387b3ab4136304b84bc98590fd4e1a75","tid":176112,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔肥就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢就好似一隻藍籌股咁<br />\n體重有上升趨勢"},{"pid":"0740b3e53a36a9888647ec2d434a0eecf38d5722","tid":176112,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9e003e310fe3392a558af5f48b6982d5e42836f","tid":176112,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同收入有咩關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食都比佢食窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9940ec6abd397d09633e902bac83fd5223cca377","tid":176112,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"終極1999 咁佢肥唔肥先"},{"pid":"f97ea6cf9a12bad057ee13f6a66b302eefaf12a5","tid":176112,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終極1999 咁佢肥唔肥先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n越來越肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae6c861e34a6b6993b73fe5cadbe1f39de98980","tid":176112,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:01:54.000Z","msg":"又話aa<br />\n人地有俾錢你理得佢食屎<br />\n食野又唔俾<br />\n麻鳩煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49955a048f48824266d6f7ef82a1684da61301f7","tid":176112,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:02:32.000Z","msg":"不如講女朋友幾高幾重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3ebc196bd0aee74c8511f1bf07289ed16908af","tid":176112,"uid":75636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:03:59.000Z"